Cora and Dana play a game where they take turns rolling a standard die. If a player rolls $n$, she is awarded $g(n)$ points, where  
\[ g(n) = \left\{
\begin{array}{cl}
8 & \text{ if } n \text{ is a multiple of 3 and 2}, \\
4 & \text{ if } n \text{ is a multiple of 3 but not of 2}, \\
3 & \text{ if } n \text{ is only a multiple of 2}, \\
1 & \text{ if } n \text{ is not a multiple of 2 or 3}.
\end{array}
\right.\]
